# Copy to .env.local and set a real value before deploying.
# Never commit .env.local — it's gitignored.

# 4-digit PIN gating /operator and /remote. Checked server-side only
# (app/api/auth/route.ts) — never sent to the client bundle. Falls back to
# 0065 if unset, which is fine for local development only.
#
# This is a convenience gate for a small trusted crew, not real
# authentication: no hashing, no rate limiting, no per-user accounts. See
# docs/DEPLOYMENT.md for what a production-grade version would add.
OPERATOR_PIN=0065
